							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-3">Responsible AI</h3>
					<ul class="text-slate-700 text-sm space-y-2">
						<li>â€¢ Technical and governance imperative</li>
						<li>â€¢ Nine dimensions: transparency, privacy, accountability, safety, inclusion, sustainability</li>
						<li>â€¢ Need machine-readable standards, open tools, and cross-sector coordination</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<!-- Model Collaboration Summary -->
				<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-emerald-100 rounded-xl p-6 border border-emerald-200">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-3">Model Collaboration & Openness</h3>
					<ul class="text-slate-700 text-sm space-y-2">
						<li>â€¢ Counter 'open-washing' with verifiable openness across models, data, and compute</li>
						<li>â€¢ Adopt permissive licensing and Model Openness Framework (Class Iâ€“III)</li>
						<li>â€¢ Broaden access to datasets and compute; preserve linguistic/cultural diversity</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<!-- Maturity & Evaluation Summary -->
				<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-50 to-orange-100 rounded-xl p-6 border border-orange-200">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-orange-900 mb-3">Maturity & Evaluation</h3>
					<ul class="text-slate-700 text-sm space-y-2">
						<li>â€¢ AI maturity and evaluation remain fragmented; focus on human-centered value</li>
						<li>â€¢ Standardize audits/testing; context-aware metrics and open tools</li>
						<li>â€¢ Prioritize real-world impact over hype; augment humans vs. blind automation</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<!-- Social & Economic Impact Summary -->
				<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-purple-100 rounded-xl p-6 border border-purple-200">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-purple-900 mb-3">Social & Economic Impact</h3>
					<ul class="text-slate-700 text-sm space-y-2">
						<li>â€¢ Tackle inequities in access, talent, and infrastructureâ€”especially in the Global South</li>
						<li>â€¢ Leverage open systems to reduce information asymmetries</li>
						<li>â€¢ Finance and climate use-cases need transparent, nonâ€“black-box approaches</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<!-- Agentic AI Summary -->
				<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 to-red-100 rounded-xl p-6 border border-red-200">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-red-900 mb-3">Agentic AI & Trust</h3>
					<ul class="text-slate-700 text-sm space-y-2">
						<li>â€¢ Agents amplify risks (misinfo, identity spoofing, unauthorized actions)</li>
						<li>â€¢ Build trust via identity, provenance (C2PA), content credentials, and standards</li>
						<li>â€¢ Architect for accountability, oversight, and secure delegation</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Five Key Themes -->
	<section id="themes" class="py-20 bg-white">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 scroll-animate">
			<div class="text-center mb-16">
				<h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">{t('themes.title')}</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
					{t('hero.description')}
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
				<!-- Responsible AI -->
				<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-blue-100 rounded-xl p-8 hover-lift scroll-animate transition-all duration-300">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
