								<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Identity & Provenance</span>
								<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">FINOS Governance</span>
